Strings.DialogImportExtensionErrorAlreadyImporte: The extension has already been imported.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionErrorDirectoryMulti: The directory contains multiple extensions. A directory must contain only one extension.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionErrorDirectoryNoExt: No extension found in the directory.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionErrorDuplicateImpor: Another extension with the same name is being imported.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionErrorItemNotFound: Could not find or access the file.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionErrorNameMismatch: The file name of the extension mismatches with its assembly name. Renaming the files in an extension is not supported.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionNotice:
You are trying to import the following extensions.
Warning: Extensions can modify the behavior of the application. Malicious extensions can harm the safety of your device.
DO NOT import extensions from untrusted sources!
Strings.DialogImportExtensionNoticeDowngrade: Some existing extensions are being downgraded. Their settings will be reset.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionNoticeReplace: Some existing extensions are being replaced. Restart will be required for this to take effect.
Strings.DialogImportExtensionNoticeSameVersion: Some existing extensions are being replaced by different versions with the same version numbers.
